    {
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "Seviyan Kheer or vermicelli pudding is a simple and well known Indian dessert in all households. It is the easiest dessert that one can make. The main ingredient is vermicelli and milk."
    },
    {
      "recipeDescriptionLine": "I have used store brought vermicelli which is widely used by all, but some experts make vermicelli at home too. I am yet to learn to make them."
    }
